targets.rawSql:
select  CONCAT (host, '___', ordem , '___', tipo,  '___', ip,  '___', name) as "DADOS", now() as time
from (
select   hg.groupid
, htg.name as grupo
, h.name
, int.ip
, h.host
, lower(hi.type) as tipo
, hi.type_full, case when hi.type_full = 'SC' then 1 when hi.type_full = 'DC' then 2 when hi.type_full = 'SR' then 3 else 4 end as ordem
, h.status
from
  host_inventory hi
, hosts_groups hg
    , hstgrp htg
, hosts h
, interface int
where
    hi.hostid = h.hostid
and hg.groupid = htg.groupid
and hg.hostid = h.hostid
and int.hostid = h.hostid
and htg.name ~ '^LAN/MODELO'
and h.name !~ 'EADI|RANEXA'
and int.ip !~ '127.0.0.1'
and h.status = 0 order by ordem) t
where grupo ~* 'LAN/MODELO/$uf/$rede' order by ordem, tipo desc ;

select  
	   split_part(grupo,'/',4) as "REDE" from 
	   (select 
		  hg.groupid
		, htg.name as grupo
		, h.name
		, int.ip
		, h.host
		, lower(hi.type) as tipo
		, hi.type_full
		, case when hi.type_full = 'SC' then 1 when hi.type_full = 'DC' then 2 else 3 end as ordem
		, h.status from host_inventory hi
		, hosts_groups hg
		, hstgrp htg
		, hosts h
		, interface int where 
		    hi.hostid = h.hostid 
		and hg.groupid = htg.groupid 
		and hg.hostid = h.hostid 
		and int.hostid = h.hostid 
		and htg.name ~ '^LAN/MODELO' 
		and h.name !~ 'EADI|RANEXA' 
		and int.ip !~ '127.0.0.1' 
		and h.status = 0) t 
where grupo ~* 'LAN/MODELO/$uf/'  and grupo !~ 'EADI|RANEXA'  order by grupo;

list.definition:
select CONCAT(host,'__',severidade,'__',evento,'__',mensagem,'__',clock) as "FALHALAN"
from (
     select t.host,t.severidade,t.evento,a.message as mensagem,t.clock
     from (  
          select t.eventid,t.host, e.severity as severidade, t.evento, to_timestamp(e.clock) as clock
          from (
               select distinct t.eventid,t.host,t.evento
               from (
                    select distinct e.eventid, t.host, e.name as evento
                    from (
                         select distinct
                                t.triggerid
                              , h.hostid
                              , h.host
                           from hosts h, hosts_groups hg, hstgrp g, items i, functions f, triggers t
                          where t.triggerid = f.triggerid
                            and f.itemid = i.itemid
                            and i.hostid = h.hostid
                            and h.hostid = hg.hostid
                            and hg.groupid = g.groupid
                            and g.name ~ '^LAN/MODELO/$uf/$rede'
--                            and g.name ~ '^WAN/MODELO/SP'
                            and (h.status,i.status) = (0,0)
                            and t.status = 0
                            and t.value = 1
                            and t.priority in (4,5)
                    ) t, events e
                    where t.triggerid = e.objectid
                      and e.severity in (4,5)
                      and e.value = 1
                      and e.source = 0
                      and to_timestamp(e.clock) between (now() - interval '30 day') and now()
               ) t left join event_recovery r on r.eventid = t.eventid
               where r.r_eventid is null
          ) t, events e
          where e.eventid = t.eventid
     ) t left join acknowledges a on a.eventid = t.eventid
     order by t.host, t.clock desc
) t
